title: Fans in the Stands - Week 5: Broken Arrow
text:
PHOTO: Broken Arrow - Week 5 Sponsored Links 
It's another week of Fans in the Stands and it's time to crown the fifth winner of the 2015 season! 
The week five champs are the members of the Broken Arrow Jungle student section. 
GALLERY: 2015 Fans in the Stands submissions 
This is Broken Arrow's second win of the season. 
Every week make sure to send your pictures and or video to phototeam@fox23.com or drop them off on Andrew Carter's FOX23 facebook or twitter. Sign up for our FOX23 News This Morning Newsletter Sign Up
